making a single all day event:
- input event name and start date, following the format in the text fields
- toggle the all day event button on
- press create event

making a single day event:
- input event name, start date, start time, end date, end time
    - following the format in the text fields
- toggle the all day event button off if on
- press create event

changing schedule start date:
- select date from the drop downs
- press change start date